ATTRIBUTION
-----------
The CRAP metric was originally created by Alberto Savoia and Bob Evans
at Google (2007). CRAPQuants implements diagnostic frameworks derived
from works by Michael Feathers, John Ousterhout, Andrew Hunt, David
Thomas, Martin Fowler, Kent Beck, Adam Tornhill, Neal Ford, and the
SonarSource Cognitive Complexity specification by G. Ann Campbell.
